data.description: This classic all brick home is a dream come true. With four spacious bedrooms and 2 1/2 bathrooms, there is plenty of room for everyone to have their own personal space. The home is situated in the heart of Apex, a charming and thriving town in North Carolina. It is located on a quiet cul-de-sac in the desirable Vintage Grove neighborhood, providing a great environment. The timeless brick exterior adds to the charm and character of the home. New Carpet, New Paint and refinished Hardwoods. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home.
